description: The final chapter in a girl’s journey through Hell! Beyond the river Acheron lay the Gates of Hell. The river that circles the Underworld is not the last obstacle that Nancy and the archangel Lucifer would find. Will the reluctant ferryman Charon help the fugitives?
name: Part 4 (of 4)

description:
WHAT HAPPENS WHEN THE NEVER-ENDING BATTLE FOR TRUTH AND JUSTICE ENDS? 
From Collider Entertainment comes the next quantum leap forward in superheroes: HALCYON. The groundbreaking new series dares to ask: What happens when the superheroes win? What happens once there is no crime, no war? The heroes of UTOPIAN achieve their final victory only to face their greatest challenge ever. An all-star collaboration courtesy of TARA BUTTERS (TV's Reaper), MARC GUGGENHEIM (Amazing Spider-Man, Resurrection), RYAN BODENHEIM (RED MASS FOR MARS), and ALISA TAGER (Serenity).
name: Episode One

description: It's a tale out of time in the Old West when seven Squaddies come together to protect a small village from the diabolical desperado, El DOOM! Don't miss--"The MAGNIFICENT SEVEN SQUADDIES!" Plus--What does it take to get three superheroines--Wasp, Tigra, and She-Hulk--full status as official members of the SUPER HERO SQUAD...? How about saving all the Boy Squaddies from certain doom and turning back an Alien Invasion?!? Yep. That oughta do it. Read "The OLD ORDER CHANGETH!"
name: Squadettes In The Old Order Changeth...!; The Squaddie Seven!

description: From the WildStorm vaults, a tremendous array of short stories featuring an incredible line-up of the top talent in the industry is collected in one place – many for the first time ever! From original stories of super-hero hijinx, to gritty tales featuring WildStorm Universe characters, this is a must have for comics fans!
name: First Issue

description:
A year after the defeat of Professor Moriarty's revenant horde and the fire-bombing of London, restoration is well under way. Yet, from across the sea, ancient eyes cast their hungry gaze upon the still vulnerable capital…Dracula is coming!

Sherlock Holmes and Dr. Watson investigate the wreck of the ship, the Demeter – its crew missing, the corpse of its Captain lashed to the ship's wheel – and soon realize this is merely the opening salvo of war from beyond the grave! Don't miss this start to a bloodthirsty new 5-issue miniseries!
name: The Dead Travel Fast

description: The Invaders return to the scene of their darkest moment from World War II...and their most feared enemies are waiting to meet them! Warrior Woman, U-Man, Master Man and a brand new Alex Ross-designed Iron Cross would be challenge enough, but there are larger forces at work...dark forces that tip the scales against the Invaders and will turn one of them against the others by issue's end!
name: Cheating Death

description:
DOUBLE CROSSES, BLOWN UP BOATS AND BANGKOK STRIPPERS... 
Duncan, Nix and Ghislain survived it all, but will they survive what comes next? As the fallout from the failed mission continues, Duncan learns a new secret that will change everything he thought he knew about being a Triplet.

In the heart of the Andes, Lady Lotus seeks out the power of the Celestials themselves. Can Captain America stop her in time? Or will the last, unresolved case of the original Young Allies prove to be his undoing? Roger Stern (INVADERS: EVE OF DESTRUCTION), Nick Dragotta (WEB OF SPIDER-MAN) and Marco Santucci (SIEGE: SPIDER-MAN) guarantee that the answers come fast and furious in this final, fateful, earth-shattering tale -- "In the Hall of the Gods!" Guest-starring the Black Widow and the Falcon!
name: In the Hall of the Gods

description:
Overview

There's no vacation spot quite like Asgard, and when Thor is called home Nova hitches a ride, only to find the fabled realm in danger with an imposter on the throne! It's a deadly day off for the cosmic Avenger as he struggles to survive troll kings, troll warriors, troll sorcerers, and the baleful consequences of flirting with a Valkyrie!

Visionary scribe Chris Yost joins forces with rising-star artists Scott Wegener and Patrick Scherberger to assemble the greatest super heroes of all time- Iron Man! Captain America! Thor! Hulk! When the world’s most evil villains attack, Captain America and Thor must join forces to stop them! Plus, don’t miss a second story featuring everyone’s favorite archer: Hawkeye!
name: Adaption; Trust

description:
Gotham's criminal crews are scrambling after a gun that never misses, an extremely valuable firearm, for its stopping power as well as its material worth. Catwoman wants to get her claws on it, too, to reaffirm her status as the Queen of Thieves.
 
Her chief rival is someone who wants it even more passionately than she does...a man who has a reason to see this gun off the streets...the city's defender...the Batman!
name: Part 2 of 2

description:
Prelude: Ratchet

He’s a healer, a diplomat, a serious kicker of Decepticon butt – and he’s the subject of our sensational lead story, Lost In Space! The ceaseless war between the Autobots and Decepticons has spread across the universe – as mechanoid medic Ratchet is about to discover!

Beast Wars: The Gathering Part Three

An ancient race of Transformers has crashed on prehistoric Earth. Imitating the animals they find there, the heroic Maximals and evil Predacons are locked in combat – the Beast Wars! Back on Cybertron, the Predacons are preparing for a revolution that will crush the Maximals!

Transformers: Movie Prequel Part Three

There’s one mother of a story before the Transformers land on Earth in the blockbuster movie – you can find out what happened here! In part three, a few Autobots face torture at the hands of Megatron as he closes in on the location of the Allspark. It ain’t gonna be pretty!

Reprints

Reprinted stories are only a portion of their respective issues.

  • Transformers: Movie Prequel, part 1c (7 pages)
  • Beast Wars: The Gathering, part 1c (10 pages)
name: Lost in Space 1: Ratchet

description:
A royal wedding is planned for the Inhumans – but the Shi’ar Imperial Guard are crashing the party! ‘War of Kings’ explodes as the insane Emperor Vulcan attacks!

Also: The Mighty Avengers must make a big decision as Chthon’s dark power spreads across Earth: will they follow Hank Pym or Iron Man? If they choose wrongly, the world is doomed!

Includes material reprinted from War of Kings #1 and Mighty Avengers #22-23.
name: War of Kings!
